dashboard.definition:
{
  "title": "Icon Library — README",
  "description": "Complete guide to configuring the Icon Library visualization",
  "dataSources": {
    "ds_stub": {
      "type": "ds.test",
      "options": { "data": { "fields": [{"name": "stub"}], "columns": [["1"]] } },
      "name": "Stub for icon rendering"
    },
    "ds_data_driven": {
      "type": "ds.test",
      "options": {
        "data": {
          "fields": [{"name": "icon"}, {"name": "color"}, {"name": "label"}, {"name": "value"}],
          "columns": [["security"], ["#22C55E"], ["Secure"], ["95"]]
        }
      },
      "name": "Data-driven example"
    }
  },
  "defaults": {},
  "visualizations": {

    "viz_title": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "# Icon Library for Splunk Dashboard Studio\n\nA custom visualization that renders **2,500+ Material Symbols** icons with configurable color, size, background, glow, shadow, labels, alignment, rotation, and click drilldown.\n\n**Font:** [Material Symbols Outlined](https://fonts.google.com/icons) — base64-embedded, no external requests.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "fontSize": "default"
      }
    },

    "viz_demo_basic": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": { "primary": "ds_stub" },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "rocket_launch",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#06B6D4"
      }
    },
    "viz_demo_labeled": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": { "primary": "ds_stub" },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "security",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#22C55E",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "Secure",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#94A3B8",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgShape": "circle",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgColor": "#0F172A",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgPadding": "20"
      }
    },
    "viz_demo_glow": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": { "primary": "ds_stub" },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "electric_bolt",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#F59E0B",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glow": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowColor": "#F59E0B",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowSize": "18"
      }
    },
    "viz_demo_combo": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": { "primary": "ds_stub" },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconName": "shield",
        "icon_library.icon_library.iconColor": "#8B5CF6",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glow": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowColor": "#8B5CF6",
        "icon_library.icon_library.glowSize": "12",
        "icon_library.icon_library.shadow": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.shadowBlur": "10",
        "icon_library.icon_library.shadowOffsetY": "4",
        "icon_library.icon_library.showLabel": "yes",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelText": "Protected",
        "icon_library.icon_library.labelColor": "#CBD5E1",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgShape": "rounded_rect",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgColor": "#1A1A2E",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgPadding": "16",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgRadius": "14"
      }
    },
    "viz_demo_data": {
      "type": "icon_library.icon_library",
      "dataSources": { "primary": "ds_data_driven" },
      "options": {
        "backgroundColor": "transparent",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgShape": "circle",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgColor": "#164E63",
        "icon_library.icon_library.bgPadding": "18"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec1_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 1. Quick Start\n\n1. Add an **Icon Library** visualization to your Dashboard Studio panel\n2. Set **`\"backgroundColor\": \"transparent\"`** in the panel options (Dashboard Studio defaults to a dark panel background for custom vizs)\n3. Pick an icon from the **Icon (Popular)** dropdown — or type a custom name\n4. Adjust color, background, glow, and label in the formatter sidebar\n\nThe visualization works **with or without** an attached search. Without a search, it renders purely from config.\n\n> **Important:** Always add `\"backgroundColor\": \"transparent\"` to the panel `options` — otherwise the panel renders with a black/dark background.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec2_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 2. Finding Icon Names\n\nBrowse all 2,500+ icons at **[fonts.google.com/icons](https://fonts.google.com/icons)**\n\n### Syntax Rules\n\n- Use **lowercase_with_underscores** only\n- Examples: `home`, `rocket_launch`, `mode_heat_off`, `nest_thermostat`\n- Invalid characters are stripped automatically\n- Set via the **Custom Icon Name** field (overrides the dropdown)\n\n### In Dashboard Studio JSON\n\n```json\n\"options\": {\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.customIcon\": \"mode_heat_off\",\n  \"icon_library.icon_library.iconColor\": \"#EF4444\"\n}\n```\n\n### Via SPL (data-driven)\n\n```spl\n| makeresults\n| eval icon=\"security\", color=\"#22C55E\", label=\"Healthy\"\n```\n\nThe `icon`, `color`, and `label` fields override config when present.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec3_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 3. All Configuration Options\n\n### Data configurations\n\n- **`iconName`** (default: `home`) — Select from 150+ popular icons via dropdown\n- **`customIcon`** (default: empty) — Any Material Symbols name. Overrides dropdown.\n\n### Data display\n\n- **`iconSize`** (default: `0` = auto) — Fixed pixel size, or `0` to auto-scale to panel\n- **`hAlign`** (default: `center`) — Horizontal position: `left`, `center`, `right`\n- **`vAlign`** (default: `center`) — Vertical position: `top`, `center`, `bottom`\n- **`rotation`** (default: `0`) — Rotation angle in degrees (0–360)\n- **`showLabel`** (default: `no`) — Show text label below icon: `yes` / `no`\n- **`labelText`** (default: empty) — The label text to display\n- **`labelSize`** (default: `0` = auto) — Label font size in pixels, `0` for auto\n- **`labelColor`** (default: `#94A3B8`) — Label text hex color\n- **`drilldown`** (default: `no`) — Enable click events: `yes` / `no`\n- **`drilldownUrl`** (default: empty) — URL with `$icon$`, `$label$`, `$color$` tokens\n- **`drilldownNewTab`** (default: `yes`) — Open URL in new tab: `yes` / `no`",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec3b_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "### Color and style\n\n- **`iconColor`** (default: `#06B6D4`) — Hex color of the icon\n- **`bgShape`** (default: `none`) — Background shape: `none`, `circle`, `rounded_rect`, `square`\n- **`bgColor`** (default: `#1E293B`) — Background fill color (hex)\n- **`bgOpacity`** (default: `1`) — Background opacity, 0 (transparent) to 1 (opaque)\n- **`bgPadding`** (default: `16`) — Space between icon and background edge (px)\n- **`bgRadius`** (default: `12`) — Corner radius for `rounded_rect` only (px)\n- **`shadow`** (default: `no`) — Drop shadow: `yes` / `no`\n- **`shadowColor`** (default: `#000000`) — Shadow hex color\n- **`shadowBlur`** (default: `8`) — Shadow blur radius (px)\n- **`shadowOffsetX`** (default: `0`) — Shadow horizontal offset (px)\n- **`shadowOffsetY`** (default: `4`) — Shadow vertical offset (px)\n- **`glow`** (default: `no`) — Glow effect: `yes` / `no`\n- **`glowColor`** (default: `#06B6D4`) — Glow hex color\n- **`glowSize`** (default: `12`) — Glow radius (px)\n\n> **Key prefix:** All options use `icon_library.icon_library.` in Dashboard Studio JSON.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec4_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 4. Drilldown / Click Interactions\n\nTwo drilldown modes:\n\n### A) Dashboard Studio eventHandlers (recommended)\n\nSet **Enable Drilldown = Yes** and leave **Drilldown URL** empty. Then add `eventHandlers` in the JSON:\n\n```json\n\"viz_my_icon\": {\n  \"type\": \"icon_library.icon_library\",\n  \"options\": { ... },\n  \"eventHandlers\": [{\n    \"type\": \"drilldown.setToken\",\n    \"options\": {\n      \"tokens\": [{\n        \"token\": \"selected_icon\",\n        \"value\": \"$row.icon.value$\"\n      }]\n    }\n  }]\n}\n```\n\n### B) Direct URL navigation\n\nSet **Drilldown URL** to a URL with token placeholders:\n\n```\nhttps://mysplunk.com/app/search/search?q=index%3Dmain%20icon%3D$icon$\n```\n\nAvailable tokens: `$icon$`, `$label$`, `$color$` (URL-encoded).",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec5_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 5. Data-Driven Icons\n\nAttach a search that returns columns named `icon`, `color`, `label`, or `value`.\n\n```spl\n| stats count AS value BY src_ip\n| eval icon=if(value>100, \"warning\", \"check_circle\"),\n       color=if(value>100, \"#EF4444\", \"#22C55E\"),\n       label=src_ip\n| head 1\n```\n\n**SPL column effects:**\n\n- **`icon`** — Overrides the icon name (sanitized to `lowercase_underscores`)\n- **`color`** — Overrides icon color (hex value)\n- **`label`** — Sets label text and auto-enables label display\n- **`value`** — Threshold coloring: >=90 green, >=50 amber, <50 red",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec6_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 6. Dashboard Studio JSON Example\n\nFull panel with all features:\n\n```json\n\"viz_status_icon\": {\n  \"type\": \"icon_library.icon_library\",\n  \"dataSources\": { \"primary\": \"ds_health\" },\n  \"options\": {\n    \"backgroundColor\": \"transparent\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.customIcon\": \"monitor_heart\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.iconColor\": \"#22C55E\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.iconSize\": \"0\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.showLabel\": \"yes\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.labelText\": \"Healthy\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.labelColor\": \"#94A3B8\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.bgShape\": \"circle\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.bgColor\": \"#0F172A\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.bgPadding\": \"20\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.glow\": \"yes\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.glowColor\": \"#22C55E\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.glowSize\": \"12\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.shadow\": \"yes\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.shadowBlur\": \"8\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.shadowOffsetY\": \"4\",\n    \"icon_library.icon_library.drilldown\": \"yes\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n> **Important:** Always include `\"backgroundColor\": \"transparent\"` — this is a Dashboard Studio panel option (not namespaced). Without it, the panel shows a dark/black background.\n\n> **Key prefix:** All other option keys use `icon_library.icon_library.` in Dashboard Studio JSON.",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    },

    "viz_sec7_hdr": {
      "type": "splunk.markdown",
      "options": {
        "markdown": "## 7. Tips\n\n- **Auto-scaling:** Set `iconSize` and `labelSize` to `0` — the icon scales to fill the panel\n- **No search required:** The icon renders from config alone; attach a search only for data-driven overrides\n- **Background shapes** automatically encompass the icon and label\n- **Glow + Shadow** can be combined for depth effects\n- **Rotation** applies to the icon (and background if present)\n- **Alignment** lets you anchor icons in corners for layout compositions\n- **Custom icons:** Any name from [fonts.google.com/icons](https://fonts.google.com/icons) works — just use `lowercase_with_underscores`\n\n---\n\n*Version 1.3.0 — Icon Library for Splunk Dashboard Studio*",
        "fontColor": "#E2E8F0",
        "backgroundColor": "transparent"
      }
    }
  },

  "layout": {
    "type": "absolute",
    "options": {
      "width": 1440,
      "height": 3500,
      "display": "auto-scale",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent"
    },
    "globalInputs": [],
    "structure": [
      { "item": "viz_title",        "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 20,   "w": 900,  "h": 120 } },
      { "item": "viz_demo_basic",   "type": "block", "position": { "x": 960, "y": 20,  "w": 100,  "h": 100 } },
      { "item": "viz_demo_labeled", "type": "block", "position": { "x": 1070, "y": 20, "w": 100,  "h": 100 } },
      { "item": "viz_demo_glow",    "type": "block", "position": { "x": 1180, "y": 20, "w": 100,  "h": 100 } },
      { "item": "viz_demo_combo",   "type": "block", "position": { "x": 1290, "y": 20, "w": 120,  "h": 120 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec1_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 160,  "w": 1360, "h": 170 } },
      { "item": "viz_demo_data",    "type": "block", "position": { "x": 1290, "y": 160, "w": 110, "h": 110 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec2_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 350,  "w": 1360, "h": 480 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec3_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 850,  "w": 1360, "h": 460 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec3b_hdr",    "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 1330, "w": 1360, "h": 480 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec4_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 1830, "w": 1360, "h": 480 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec5_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 2330, "w": 1360, "h": 340 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec6_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 2690, "w": 1360, "h": 560 } },
      { "item": "viz_sec7_hdr",     "type": "block", "position": { "x": 40, "y": 3270, "w": 1360, "h": 200 } }
    ]
  },
  "applicationProperties": { "theme": "dark" }
}
